trans-unit.source: Represents a container for <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3D" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa um contêiner para objetos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3D" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D.Children%2A> collection of a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> element can only consist of <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> objects.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D.Children%2A> coleção de um <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> elemento pode consistir apenas de <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> objetos.

trans-unit.source: Adding a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> child to a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> implicitly adds it to the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3DCollection> for the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> element.
trans-unit.target: Adicionando um <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> filho para uma <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> adiciona implicitamente para o <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3DCollection> para o <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> elemento.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> does not have a visual representation; it serves as a container for other visual 3-D objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> não tem uma representação visual; Ele serve como um contêiner para outros objetos 3D visual.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> is a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> object, which provides support for input, focus, and events in 3-D.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> é um <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> objeto, que fornece suporte para entrada, o foco e eventos em 3D.

trans-unit.source: This class does not set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3D.Visual3DModel%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não define o <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3D.Visual3DModel%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> is introduced in the .NET Framework version 3.5.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D> é introduzido no .NET Framework versão 3.5.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
trans-unit.target: Para saber mais, confira [Versões e dependências](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
